file.name: hello.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Hello Specification
  description: This specification says Hello
  termsOfService: http://example.com/terms/
  contact:
    name: Support
    url: http://www.example.com/support/
    email: support@example.com
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html
  version: "1.0"
servers:
- url: http://api.example.com/
  description: Main server
- url: http://api.example.io/
  description: Secondary server
paths:
  /hello/{name}:
    get:
      summary: Retun an hello object
      operationId: hello
      parameters:
      - name: name
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
      - name: language
        in: query
        description: Language used to say hello
        schema:
          type: string
          enum:
          - english
          - french
          - german
          - italian
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/text:
              schema:
                type: string
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Hello'
            application/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Hello'
        "4XX":
          description: Error
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
components:
  schemas:
    Hello:
      type: object
      properties:
        timestamp:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: Unix timestamp (generation time)
        message:
          type: string
    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
